# Enterprise ERP — Master Architecture & Contract Rules

This document is the single source of truth for all frontend architecture, API contracts, permissions, error handling, environment configuration, and testing standards.

Designed for: large business systems, modular domains, long-term maintainability, AI-assisted development, high scalability, multi-team collaboration, future microservices, Turborepo compatibility.

The architecture must remain: clean, composable, modular, predictable, scalable, RTL-first, premium-quality.

---

# 1. Core Architecture Philosophy

Always prioritize: separation of concerns, composability, modularity, server-first rendering, reusable systems, predictable structure, maintainable codebases, minimal client-side JavaScript.

Avoid monolithic implementations. Large systems must be split into isolated feature modules.

---

# 2. Project Structure — صفحة مستقلة = مجلد واحد كامل (Required)

**المبدأ:** كل route له **كبسولة صفحة (page capsule)** — مجلد واحد فيه كل ما يخص هذه الصفحة: components، hooks، services، `lib/api`، types، constants، dialogs.

**القاعدة:** `features/` مرآة لـ `app/`. مثال `/hr/organization/branches` → كل ملفات الفروع داخل `features/hr/organization/branches/` وليس في `organization/lib/api/`.

